ewman\"}, {\"begin\": 617, \"end\": 623, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9976274085608321, \"rank\": 0.0023782264324737697, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 668, \"end\": 675, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9778159803048386, \"rank\": 0.022687315544744423, \"text\": \"Germany\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_women's_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In our national anthem, we talk about blood, too.\", \"from\": 678, \"to\": 728, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We are willing to spill blood on the court.\", \"from\": 729, \"to\": 772, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's no big deal.\", \"from\": 774, \"to\": 791, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If it allows us to win gold, I am all for it,\\\" Wembaynama said of the blood after the game.\", \"from\": 792, \"to\": 883, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Wembanyama had 11 points with seven rebounds and four assists in the game to set France up for a gold medal match against the U.S. on Saturday.\", \"from\": 885, \"to\": 1028, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 966, \"end\": 972, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9976274085608321, \"rank\": 0.0023782264324737697, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The U.S pulled off a fourth-quarter comeback\\u00a0against Serbia to advance to its fourth straight gold medal game, winning 95-91.\", \"from\": 1030, \"to\": 1155, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1083, \"end\": 1089, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999845224035185, \"rank\": 1.5477835257446986e-05, \"text\": \"Serbia\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Noah Lylessent a post on Instagram after finishing third in the men's 200-meter final and reports surfacing of him testing positive for COVID-19 emerged on Thursday.\", \"from\": 1157, \"to\": 1322, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1157, \"end\": 1161, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Bennet\", \"score\": 0.9987511437927384, \"rank\": 0.0010336855876287648, \"text\": \"Noah\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Bennet\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Bennet\"}, {\"begin\": 1182, \"end\": 1191, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8209077142341994e-35, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}, {\"begin\": 1293, \"end\": 1301, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic\", \"score\": 0.999996151223189, \"rank\": 3.848694770077111e-06, \"text\": \"COVID-19\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lyles thanked his supporters and other competitors while announcing that his Paris Olympics run is likely over.\", \"from\": 1323, \"to\": 1434, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"First I want to thank God for getting me through this entire Olympics!\", \"from\": 1436, \"to\": 1507, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Second I want to congratulate [Letsile Tebogo and Kenny Bednarek]\\u00a0and everyone else on an amazing Olympic 200m final.\", \"from\": 1508, \"to\": 1625, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1558, \"end\": 1572, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenny_Bednarek\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kenny Bednarek\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenny_Bednarek\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenny_Bednarek\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Finally I want to thank everyone for the supportive messages,\\\" Lyles wrote.\", \"from\": 1626, \"to\": 1701, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I believe this will be the end of my 2024 Olympics.\", \"from\": 1702, \"to\": 1754, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It is not the Olympic I dreamed of but it has left me with so much Joy in my heart.\", \"from\": 1755, \"to\": 1838, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I hope everyone enjoyed the show.\\\"\", \"from\": 1839, \"to\": 1873, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After the race, Lyles needed to be tended to by medical staff.\", \"from\": 1875, \"to\": 1937, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1891, \"end\": 1896, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trey_Lyles\", \"score\": 0.999999999998181, \"rank\": 1.7316569792993062e-12, \"text\": \"Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trey_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trey_Lyles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He was seen wearing a mask on Wednesday and before the race on Thursday.\", \"from\": 1938, \"to\": 2010, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"NBC then announced that Lyles had tested positive for COVID-19 two days earlier, finding out from his \\\"distraught\\\" mother.\", \"from\": 2011, \"to\": 2133, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2011, \"end\": 2014, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"score\": 0.9573589389988861, \"rank\": 0.04453989303215399, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\"}, {\"begin\": 2035, \"end\": 2040, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trey_Lyles\", \"score\": 0.999999999998181, \"rank\": 1.7316569792993062e-12, \"text\": \"Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trey_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trey_Lyles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"USA Track and Field confirmed the positive case to the BBC.\", \"from\": 2134, \"to\": 2193, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2134, \"end\": 2137, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.9999846765259361, \"rank\": 9.797342592846219e-06, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2189, \"end\": 2192, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"score\": 0.9999764057775309, \"rank\": 2.359476108040885e-05, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He is also asthmatic.\", \"from\": 2194, \"to\": 2215, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Lyles' reaction time of 0.173 was the slowest of the eight runners in the race.\", \"from\": 2217, \"to\": 2296, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He was tied for the slowest reaction time in the men's 100m, as well, but he still managed to pull off a personal best of 9.79, winning by five-thousandths of a second.\", \"from\": 2297, \"to\": 2465, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Of course, that was before he was sick.\", \"from\": 2466, \"to\": 2505, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Lyles message suggests he will likely not participate in the upcoming men's 4x100 meter relay.\", \"from\": 2507, \"to\": 2601, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He leaves Paris having won the United States'\\u00a0first gold medal\\u00a0in the men's 100m since 2004.\", \"from\": 2603, \"to\": 2695, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2613, \"end\": 2618, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0214308004096505e-16, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2634, \"end\": 2647, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.035305574085896e-13, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ryan Morik contributed to this report.\", \"from\": 2697, \"to\": 2735, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2697, \"end\": 2701, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"score\": 0.999999999996362, \"rank\": 2.216392100181983e-12, \"text\": \"Ryan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"American hurdler Grant Holloway won his first Olympic gold medal in Paris on Thursday.\", \"from\": 2737, \"to\": 2823, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2737, \"end\": 2745, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999985652604043, \"rank\": 1.4344359790087024e-06, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"beg